Sophie Renoir https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sophie_Renoir 0 Sophie Renoir (born 1964) is a French actress. She is the great-granddaughter of the French Impressionist painter Pierre-Auguste Renoir (1841-1919), and daughter of the cinematographer Claude Renoir (1913–93). In 1988, she was nominated for César Award for Most Promising Actress for her part in Boyfriends and Girlfriends by Eric Rohmer. Sophie_Renoir ( born 1964 ) is a_French_actress .
